pageContext.claim: “I mean, give me a break. They're political hacks. So you look at it -- I mean, you have [John] Brennan, you have [James] Clapper, and you have [James] Comey. Comey is proven now to be a liar and he's proven to be a leaker.”
pageContext.analysis: Brennan, Clapper and Comey spent their professional lives in the intelligence and law enforcement worlds and thus are not political hacks. There is no proof that Comey lied about his interactions with Trump.
